ce the M~31 nuclear-disk photometry and mean\nstellar velocity, including the observed asymmetries. It requires a central\nmass concentration and a cold disk system representing between 20 and 40% of\nits mass. Abridged..\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 27 Oct 2000 17:05:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 23 Feb 2001 16:50:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-10-31"}
