st that most of the ISM in the LMC is fractal,\npresumably the result of pervasive turbulence, self-gravity, and self-similar\nstirring.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 27 Oct 2000 20:26:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-10-13"}
